{
  "texts": [
    "For the upcoming CMIP7 an updated solar forcing dataset is currently in preparation [168].",
    "For future climate projections, it is essential to have a robust future scenario of solar irradiance available.",
    "Forecasting solar variability is challenging due to the complex nature of the Sun.",
    "Traditional methods, such as empirical models [169], have been employed to predict solar forcing.",
    "Nevertheless, these approaches often have limitations in accurately capturing the intricate dynamics of the Sun."
  ]
}